result.title: 1985 - 2015 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Reconstruction of North Sea trawling effort 1985-2015
result.name: 1985-2015-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-reconstruction-o-1985-2015
result.notes:
Spatial distribution of total international otter and beam trawling fishing 
effort, for all ICES rectangles (0.5 degree latitude by 1 degree longitude) of 
the North Sea, covering a 31-year time span from 1985 to 2015. The dataset was 
largely reconstructed using compiled effort data from 7 fishing effort 
time-series and completed by estimations of missing data. Lat and Long 
coordinates in the data represent the centre of each ICES rectangle.
